  "id": "RAW_f76cf472",
  "title": "云 CISO 视角 ：2025 年回顾：云安全基础与不断发展的人工智能",
  "url": "https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-2025-in-review-cloud-security-basics-and-evolving-ai/",
  "date": "2025-12-20 00:00:00",
  "author": "Nick Godfrey, Anton Chuvakin",
  "siteName": "Google Cloud Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <p>Welcome to the second Cloud CISO Perspectives for December 2025. Today, Google Cloud’s Nick Godfrey, senior director, and Anton Chuvakin, security advisor, look back at the year that was.</p>\n    <p>As with all Cloud CISO Perspectives, the contents of this newsletter are posted to the <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/\" track-name=\"google cloud blog\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/\">Google Cloud blog</a>. If you’re reading this on the website and you’d like to receive the email version, you can <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/resources/google-cloud-ciso-newsletter-signup\" track-name=\"subscribe here\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/resources/google-cloud-ciso-newsletter-signup\">subscribe here</a>.</p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"k6ctOd\">\n   <aside class=\"IwVNTb\">\n    <div class=\"ecJG2e nRhiJb-ObfsIf\">\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-qWD73c nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf-V2iZpe nRhiJb-snVHke-ibL1re-X66g3b nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-UFsB2c\">\n      <h4 class=\"Qwf2Db-MnozTc Qwf2Db-MnozTc-OWXEXe-MnozTc-qWD73c\">Get vital board insights with Google Cloud</h4>\n      <div class=\"nRhiJb-qJTHM nRhiJb-DbgRPb-R6PoUb-ma6Yeb\">\n       <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n        <p>Our curated insights hub for boards of directors highlights resources on cybersecurity, risk governance, and security transformation, including the latest blogs and research from Google Cloud.</p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"nRhiJb-LgbsSe  nRhiJb-LgbsSe-OWXEXe-MNynB-o6Shpd LZTd1c\" href=\"https://cloud.google.com/solutions/security/board-of-directors?utm_source=cloud_sfdc&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=FY24-Q2-global-PROD941-physicalevent-er-CEG_Boardroom_Summit&amp;utm_content=-&amp;utm_term=-\" track-name=\"visit the hub\" track-type=\"button\" track-metadata-position=\"body\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/solutions/security/board-of-directors?utm_source=cloud_sfdc&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=FY24-Q2-global-PROD941-physicalevent-er-CEG_Boardroom_Summit&amp;utm_content=-&amp;utm_term=-\" track-metadata-module=\"aside\" track-metadata-module_headline=\"get vital board insights with google cloud\">Visit the hub </a>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-ibL1re nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf-V2iZpe nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-X66g3b gHo9yf\">\n      <section class=\"PBkdHd \">\n       <img class=\" IIal6e\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/GCAT-replacement-logo-A_6pb928M.max-600x600.png\" alt=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/GCAT-replacement-logo-A_6pb928M.max-600x600.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </section>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </aside>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <h3 class=\"MnozTc-Bz112c MnozTc-Bz112c-OWXEXe-R6PoUb\">2025 in review: Highlighting cloud security and evolving AI</h3>\n    <p><i>By Nick Godfrey, senior director, and Anton Chuvakin, security advisor, Office of the CISO</i></p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div>\n    <section class=\"PBkdHd DhGbH\" jscontroller=\"SCGBie\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\">\n     <img class=\"JcsBte JNiM6e Yhj9ne\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/NickGodfrey8975-hi_Tm5UVy8.max-2200x2200.jpg\" alt=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/NickGodfrey8975-hi_Tm5UVy8.max-2200x2200.jpg\" jsname=\"P3Vluc\" jsaction=\"click:HTIlC\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </section>\n    <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n     <p>Cybersecurity is facing a unique moment, where AI-enhanced threat intelligence, products, and services have begun to give defenders an advantage over the threats they face that had proven elusive — until now.</p>\n     <p>However, threat actors have also begun to take advantage of AI in ways that have moved towards a wider use of tools.</p>\n     <p>At Google Cloud, we continue to strive towards our goals of bringing simplicity, streamlining operations, and enhancing efficiency and effectiveness for security essentials. AI is now part of that essential security approach, both building AI securely and using AI to boost defenders.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div>\n    <section class=\"PBkdHd DhGbH\" jscontroller=\"SCGBie\" jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\">\n     <img class=\"JcsBte JNiM6e Yhj9ne\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/Anton_Chuvakin_Headshot_18L8044_SQ1_Hi_Res.max-2200x2200.jpg\" alt=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/Anton_Chuvakin_Headshot_18L8044_SQ1_Hi_Res.max-2200x2200.jpg\" jsname=\"P3Vluc\" jsaction=\"click:HTIlC\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </section>\n    <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n     <p>Looking back at 2025, we’re sharing our top stories across five vital areas of development in cybersecurity: securing cloud, securing AI, AI-enabled defense, threat intelligence, and building the most trusted cloud.</p>\n     <p><b>Securing cloud</b></p>\n     <p>This year reinforced the importance of cloud security fundamentals. Cybersecurity risks continue to accelerate with the number and severity of breaches continuing to grow, and more organizations are turning to multi-cloud and hybrid solutions that introduce their own complex management challenges.</p>\n     <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/google-announces-agreement-acquire-wiz/\" track-name=\"google announces agreement to acquire wiz\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/google-announces-agreement-acquire-wiz/\">Google announces agreement to acquire Wiz</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/responding-to-cve-2025-55182/\" track-name=\"responding to cve-2025-55182: secure your react and next.js workloads\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/responding-to-cve-2025-55182/\">Responding to CVE-2025-55182: Secure your React and Next.js workloads</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/google-advances-sovereignty-choice-and-security-in-the-cloud/\" track-name=\"google advances sovereignty, choice, and security in the cloud\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/google-advances-sovereignty-choice-and-security-in-the-cloud/\">Google advances sovereignty, choice, and security in the cloud</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/prove-your-expertise-with-our-new-secops-engineer-certification/\" track-name=\"prove your expertise with our new secops engineer certification\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/prove-your-expertise-with-our-new-secops-engineer-certification/\">Prove your expertise with our new SecOps engineer certification</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/project-shield-blocked-a-massive-recent-ddos-attack-heres-how/\" track-name=\"project shield blocked a massive recent ddos attack. here’s how\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/project-shield-blocked-a-massive-recent-ddos-attack-heres-how/\">Project Shield blocked a massive recent DDoS attack. Here’s how</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/secure-cloud-insecure-use-and-what-you-can-do-about-it/\" track-name=\"secure cloud. insecure use. (and what you can do about it)\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/secure-cloud-insecure-use-and-what-you-can-do-about-it/\">Secure cloud. Insecure use. (And what you can do about it)</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/how-google-does-it-modernizing-threat-detection/\" track-name=\"how google does it: modernizing threat detection\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/how-google-does-it-modernizing-threat-detection/\">How Google Does It: Modernizing threat detection</a></li>\n     </ul>\n     <p><b>Securing AI</b></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <p>2025 was a crucial year as we continued our efforts to build AI securely — and to encourage others to do so, too. From AI governance to building agents securely, we wanted to give our customers the tools they need to secure their AI supply chain and tools.</p>\n    <ul>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-boards-should-be-bilingual-AI-security-gain-advantage\" track-name=\"boards should be ‘bilingual’ in ai, security to gain advantage\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-boards-should-be-bilingual-AI-security-gain-advantage\">Boards should be ‘bilingual’ in AI, security to gain advantage</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-5-tips-secure-ai-success\" track-name=\"5 tips for secure ai success\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-5-tips-secure-ai-success\">5 tips for secure AI success</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/introducing-ai-protection-security-for-the-ai-era/\" track-name=\"introducing ai protection: security for the ai era\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/introducing-ai-protection-security-for-the-ai-era/\">Introducing AI Protection: Security for the AI era</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/same-same-but-also-different-google-guidance-ai-supply-chain-security/\" track-name=\"google guidance on securing your ai supply chain\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/same-same-but-also-different-google-guidance-ai-supply-chain-security/\">Google guidance on securing your AI supply chain</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-how-google-secures-ai-agents\" track-name=\"how google secures ai agents\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-how-google-secures-ai-agents\">How Google secures AI agents</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/ai-agent-security-how-to-protect-digital-sidekicks-and-your-business/\" track-name=\"ai agent security: how to protect digital sidekicks (and your business)\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/ai-agent-security-how-to-protect-digital-sidekicks-and-your-business/\">AI agent security: How to protect digital sidekicks (and your business)</a></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><b>AI-enabled defense</b></p>\n    <p>We have seen some incredible strides towards empowering defenders with AI this year. As defenders guide others on how to secure their use of AI, we must ensure that we also use AI to support stronger defensive action.</p>\n    <ul>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-our-big-sleep-agent-makes-big-leap\" track-name=\"our big sleep agent makes a big leap\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-our-big-sleep-agent-makes-big-leap\">Our Big Sleep agent makes a big leap</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/3-new-ways-ai-security-sidekick\" track-name=\"3 new ways to use ai as your security sidekick\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/3-new-ways-ai-security-sidekick\">3 new ways to use AI as your security sidekick</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/how-google-does-it-building-ai-agents-cybersecurity-defense/\" track-name=\"how google does it: building ai agents for cybersecurity and defense\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/how-google-does-it-building-ai-agents-cybersecurity-defense/\">How Google Does It: Building AI agents for cybersecurity and defense</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-ai-strategic-imperative-to-manage-risk\" track-name=\"ai as a strategic imperative to manage risk\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-ai-strategic-imperative-to-manage-risk\">AI as a strategic imperative to manage risk</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/beyond-the-hype-analyzing-new-data-on-roi-of-ai-in-security\" track-name=\"beyond the hype: analyzing new data on roi of ai in security\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/beyond-the-hype-analyzing-new-data-on-roi-of-ai-in-security\">Beyond the hype: Analyzing new data on ROI of AI in security</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/the-dawn-of-agentic-ai-in-security-operations-at-rsac-2025\" track-name=\"the dawn of agentic ai in security operations at rsac 2025\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/the-dawn-of-agentic-ai-in-security-operations-at-rsac-2025\">The dawn of agentic AI in security operations at RSAC 2025</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/introducing-the-agentic-soc-workshops-for-security-professionals/\" track-name=\"introducing the agentic soc workshops for security professionals\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/introducing-the-agentic-soc-workshops-for-security-professionals/\">Introducing the Agentic SOC Workshops for security professionals</a></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><b>Threat intelligence</b></p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <p>As defenders have made significant advances in using AI to boost their efforts this year, government-backed threat actors and cybercriminals have been trying to do the same. At Google, we strongly believe in the power of threat intelligence to enhance defender abilities to respond to critical threats faster and more efficiently.</p>\n    <ul>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/ultimate-insider-threat-north-korean-it-workers/\" track-name=\"the ultimate insider threat: north korean it workers\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/ultimate-insider-threat-north-korean-it-workers/\">The ultimate insider threat: North Korean IT workers</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-recent-advances-in-how-threat-actors-use-ai-tools\" track-name=\"recent advances in how threat actors use ai tools\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-recent-advances-in-how-threat-actors-use-ai-tools\">Recent advances in how threat actors use AI tools</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-new-ai-cybercrime-reports-underscore-need-security-best-practices\" track-name=\"new ai, cybercrime reports underscore need for security best practices\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-new-ai-cybercrime-reports-underscore-need-security-best-practices\">New AI, cybercrime reports underscore need for security best practices</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-how-ciso-board-can-fight-cyber-enabled-fraud/\" track-name=\"how cisos and boards can help fight cyber-enabled fraud\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-how-ciso-board-can-fight-cyber-enabled-fraud/\">How CISOs and boards can help fight cyber-enabled fraud</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/how-google-does-it-threat-intelligence-uncover-track-cybercrime\" track-name=\"how google does it: using threat intelligence to uncover and track cybercrime\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/how-google-does-it-threat-intelligence-uncover-track-cybercrime\">How Google Does It: Using threat intelligence to uncover and track cybercrime</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/how-to-build-best-practice-cyber-threat-intelligence-program\" track-name=\"how to build a best-practice cyber threat intelligence program\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/how-to-build-best-practice-cyber-threat-intelligence-program\">How to build a best-practice Cyber Threat Intelligence program</a></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><b>Building the most trusted cloud</b></p>\n    <p>We continued to enhance our security capabilities and controls on our cloud platform to help organizations secure their cloud environments and address evolving policy, compliance, and business objectives.</p>\n    <ul>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/announcing-the-google-unified-security-recommended-program/\" track-name=\"announcing the google unified security recommended program\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/announcing-the-google-unified-security-recommended-program/\">Announcing the Google Unified Security Recommended program</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/driving-secure-innovation-with-ai-google-unified-security-next25\" track-name=\"next ‘25: driving secure innovation with google unified security\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/driving-secure-innovation-with-ai-google-unified-security-next25\">Next ‘25: Driving secure innovation with Google Unified Security</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/security-summit-2025-enabling-defenders-and-securing-ai-innovation/\" track-name=\"security summit 2025: enabling defenders and securing ai innovation\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/security-summit-2025-enabling-defenders-and-securing-ai-innovation/\">Security Summit 2025: Enabling defenders and securing AI innovation</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-disrupt-ransomware-ai-google-drive\" track-name=\"disrupt ransomware with ai in google drive\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-disrupt-ransomware-ai-google-drive\">Disrupt ransomware with AI in Google Drive</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/enabling-a-safe-agentic-web-with-recaptcha/\" track-name=\"enabling a safe agentic web with recaptcha\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/enabling-a-safe-agentic-web-with-recaptcha/\">Enabling a safe agentic web with reCAPTCHA</a></li>\n     <li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/mastering-secure-ai-on-google-cloud-a-practical-guide-for-enterprises\" track-name=\"mastering secure ai on google cloud: a practical guide for enterprises\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/mastering-secure-ai-on-google-cloud-a-practical-guide-for-enterprises\">Mastering secure AI on Google Cloud: A practical guide for enterprises</a></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p><b>Our forecast for 2026</b></p>\n    <p>As security professionals, we know that threat actors will continue to innovate to achieve their mission objectives. To help defenders proactively prepare for the coming year, we publish our annual forecast report with <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-our-2026-cybersecurity-forecast-report\" track-name=\"insights from across google\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/cloud-ciso-perspectives-our-2026-cybersecurity-forecast-report\">insights from across Google</a>. We look forward to sharing more insights to help organizations strengthen their security posture in the new year.</p>\n    <p><i>For more leadership guidance from Google Cloud experts, please visit our</i> <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/solutions/security/leaders\" track-name=\"ciso insights hub\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/solutions/security/leaders\"><i>CISO Insights hub</i></a><i>.</i></p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"k6ctOd\">\n   <aside class=\"IwVNTb\">\n    <div class=\"ecJG2e nRhiJb-ObfsIf\">\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-qWD73c nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf-V2iZpe nRhiJb-snVHke-ibL1re-X66g3b nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-UFsB2c\">\n      <h4 class=\"Qwf2Db-MnozTc Qwf2Db-MnozTc-OWXEXe-MnozTc-qWD73c\">Learn something new</h4>\n      <div class=\"nRhiJb-qJTHM nRhiJb-DbgRPb-R6PoUb-ma6Yeb\">\n       <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n        <p>Lloyds Banking Group, the biggest digital bank in the U.K., transforms security into high gain, low grind with Google Security Operations.</p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"nRhiJb-LgbsSe  nRhiJb-LgbsSe-OWXEXe-MNynB-o6Shpd LZTd1c\" href=\"https://youtu.be/7gNyN3fBn00?si=Lgrxi9908i-IvAHP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" track-name=\"watch now\" track-type=\"button\" track-metadata-position=\"body\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"youtu.be/7gNyN3fBn00?si=Lgrxi9908i-IvAHP\" track-metadata-module=\"aside\" track-metadata-module_headline=\"learn something new\">Watch now </a>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-ibL1re nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf-V2iZpe nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-X66g3b gHo9yf\">\n      <section class=\"PBkdHd \">\n       <img class=\" IIal6e\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/GCAT-replacement-logo-A.max-600x600.png\" alt=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/GCAT-replacement-logo-A.max-600x600.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </section>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </aside>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <h3 class=\"MnozTc-Bz112c MnozTc-Bz112c-OWXEXe-ibL1re\"><b>In case you missed it</b></h3>\n    <p>Here are the latest updates, products, services, and resources from our security teams so far this month:</p>\n    <ul>\n     <li><b>How Google Does It: Collecting and analyzing cloud forensics</b>: Here’s how Google’s Incident Management and Digital Forensics team gathers and analyzes digital evidence. <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/how-google-does-it-collecting-and-analyzing-cloud-forensics\" track-name=\"read more\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/how-google-does-it-collecting-and-analyzing-cloud-forensics\"><b>Read more</b></a>.</li>\n     <li><b>When securing Web3, remember your Web2 fundamentals</b>: As Web3 matures, the stakes continue to rise. For Web3 to thrive, security should expand beyond the blockchain to protect operational infrastructure. Here’s how. <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/transform/when-securing-web3-remember-your-web2-fundamentals/\" track-name=\"read more\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/transform/when-securing-web3-remember-your-web2-fundamentals/\"><b>Read more</b></a>.</li>\n     <li><b>How Mandiant can help test and strengthen your cyber resilience</b>: To help teams better prepare for actual incidents, we developed ThreatSpace, a cyber proving ground with all the digital noise of real employee activities. <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/how-mandiant-can-help-test-and-strengthen-your-cyber-resilience/\" track-name=\"read more\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security/how-mandiant-can-help-test-and-strengthen-your-cyber-resilience/\"><b>Read more</b></a>.</li>\n     <li><b>Exploiting agency of autonomous AI agents with task injection</b>: Learn what a task injection attack is, how it differs from prompt injection, and how it is particularly relevant to AI agents designed for a wide range of actions and tasks, such as computer-use agents. <a href=\"https://bughunters.google.com/blog/4823857172971520/task-injection-exploiting-agency-of-autonomous-ai-agents\" target=\"_blank\" track-name=\"read more\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"bughunters.google.com/blog/4823857172971520/task-injection-exploiting-agency-of-autonomous-ai-agents\" rel=\"opener\"><b>Read more</b></a>.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Please visit the Google Cloud blog for more security stories <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security\" track-name=\"published this month\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/products/identity-security\">published this month</a>.</p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"k6ctOd\">\n   <aside class=\"IwVNTb\">\n    <div class=\"ecJG2e nRhiJb-ObfsIf\">\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-qWD73c nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf-V2iZpe nRhiJb-snVHke-ibL1re-X66g3b nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-UFsB2c\">\n      <h4 class=\"Qwf2Db-MnozTc Qwf2Db-MnozTc-OWXEXe-MnozTc-qWD73c\">Join the Google Cloud CISO Community</h4>\n      <div class=\"nRhiJb-qJTHM nRhiJb-DbgRPb-R6PoUb-ma6Yeb\">\n       <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n        <p>At Google Cloud, we have discussed with great interest from security leaders how to move from artisanal security to operating at industrial scale. Please join us as we shift the conversation to explore how organizations can refine and optimize their security approach to thrive in today’s environment.</p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <a class=\"nRhiJb-LgbsSe  nRhiJb-LgbsSe-OWXEXe-MNynB-o6Shpd LZTd1c\" href=\"https://rsvp.withgoogle.com/events/ciso-community-interest?utm_source=cgc-blog&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=2024-cloud-ciso-newsletter-events-ref&amp;utm_content=-&amp;utm_term=-\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" track-name=\"learn more\" track-type=\"button\" track-metadata-position=\"body\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"rsvp.withgoogle.com/events/ciso-community-interest?utm_source=cgc-blog&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=2024-cloud-ciso-newsletter-events-ref&amp;utm_content=-&amp;utm_term=-\" track-metadata-module=\"aside\" track-metadata-module_headline=\"join the google cloud ciso community\">Learn more </a>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-ibL1re nRhiJb-kR0ZEf-OWXEXe-GV1x9e-OiUrBf-V2iZpe nRhiJb-snVHke-R6PoUb-X66g3b gHo9yf\">\n      <section class=\"PBkdHd \">\n       <img class=\" IIal6e\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/GCAT-replacement-logo-A_6pb928M.max-600x600.png\" alt=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-cloudblog-publish/images/GCAT-replacement-logo-A_6pb928M.max-600x600.png\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </section>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </aside>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <h3 class=\"MnozTc-Bz112c MnozTc-Bz112c-OWXEXe-c5RTEf\"><b>Threat Intelligence news</b></h3>\n    <ul>\n     <li><b>How threat actors are exploiting React2Shell</b>: Shortly after CVE-2025-55182 was disclosed, Google Threat Intelligence Group (GTIG) began observing widespread exploitation across many threat clusters, from opportunistic cybercrime actors to suspected espionage groups. Here’s what GTIG has observed so far. <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/threat-actors-exploit-react2shell-cve-2025-55182\" track-name=\"read more\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/threat-actors-exploit-react2shell-cve-2025-55182\"><b>Read more</b></a><b>.</b></li>\n     <li><b>Intellexa’s prolific zero-day exploits continue</b>: Despite extensive scrutiny and public reporting, commercial surveillance vendors such as Intellexa continue to operate unimpeded. Known for its “Predator” spyware, new GTIG analysis shows that Intellexa is evading restrictions and thriving. <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/intellexa-zero-day-exploits-continue\" track-name=\"read more\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/intellexa-zero-day-exploits-continue\"><b>Read more</b></a><b>.</b></li>\n     <li><b>APT24's pivot to multi-vector attacks</b>: GTIG is tracking a long-running and adaptive cyber espionage campaign by APT24, a People's Republic of China (PRC)-nexus threat actor that has been deploying BADAUDIO over the past three years. Here’s our analysis of the campaign and malware, and how defenders can detect and mitigate this persistent threat. <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/apt24-pivot-to-multi-vector-attacks\" track-name=\"read more\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/apt24-pivot-to-multi-vector-attacks\"><b>Read more</b></a><b>.</b></li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>Please visit the Google Cloud blog for more threat intelligence stories <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/\" track-name=\"published this month\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/blog/topics/threat-intelligence/\">published this month</a>.</p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"Wy08Ac nRhiJb-qJTHM-OWXEXe-hJDwNd nRhiJb-DbgRPb-II5mzb-cGMI2b\">\n   <div jsaction=\"rcuQ6b:npT2md\" jscontroller=\"M0Q3Qb\" data-is-cws-richtext=\"true\" class=\" \">\n    <h3 class=\"MnozTc-Bz112c MnozTc-Bz112c-OWXEXe-II5mzb\"><b>Now hear this: Podcasts from Google Cloud</b></h3>\n    <ul>\n     <li><b>Bruce Schneier on the AI offense-defense balance</b>: From rewiring democracy to hacking trust, Bruce Schneier discusses the impact of AI on society with hosts Anton Chuvakin and Tim Peacock. Hear his take on whether it will help support liberal democracy more, or boost the forces of corruption, illiberalism, and authoritarianism. <a href=\"https://cloud.withgoogle.com/cloudsecurity/podcast/ep256-rewiring-democracy-hacking-trust-bruce-schneier-on-the-ai-offense-defense-balance/\" target=\"_blank\" track-name=\"listen here\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.withgoogle.com/cloudsecurity/podcast/ep256-rewiring-democracy-hacking-trust-bruce-schneier-on-the-ai-offense-defense-balance/\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>Listen here</b></a>.</li>\n     <li><b>The truth about autonomous AI hacking</b>: Heather Adkins, Google’s Security Engineering vice-president, separates the hype from the hazards of autonomous AI hacking, with Anton and Tim. <a href=\"https://cloud.withgoogle.com/cloudsecurity/podcast/ep255-separating-hype-from-hazard-the-truth-about-autonomous-ai-hacking/\" target=\"_blank\" track-name=\"listen here\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.withgoogle.com/cloudsecurity/podcast/ep255-separating-hype-from-hazard-the-truth-about-autonomous-ai-hacking/\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>Listen here</b></a>.</li>\n     <li><b>Escaping 1990s vulnerability management</b>: Caleb Hoch, consulting manager for security transformations, Mandiant, discusses with Anton and Tim how vulnerability management has evolved beyond basic scanning and reporting, and the biggest gaps between modern practices and what organizations are actually doing. <a href=\"https://cloud.withgoogle.com/cloudsecurity/podcast/ep254-escaping-1990s-vulnerability-management-from-unauthenticated-scans-to-ai-driven-mitigation/\" target=\"_blank\" track-name=\"listen here\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.withgoogle.com/cloudsecurity/podcast/ep254-escaping-1990s-vulnerability-management-from-unauthenticated-scans-to-ai-driven-mitigation/\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>Listen here</b></a>.</li>\n     <li><b>Adopting a dual offensive-defensive mindset</b>: Betty DeVita, private and public board director and fintech advisor, shares her take on how boards can take on an offensive and defensive approach to cybersecurity for their organizations. <a href=\"https://cybersavvyboardroom.libsyn.com/ep11-betty-devita-on-adopting-an-offensive-and-defensive-mindset\" target=\"_blank\" track-name=\"listen here\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cybersavvyboardroom.libsyn.com/ep11-betty-devita-on-adopting-an-offensive-and-defensive-mindset\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>Listen here</b></a>.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p>To have our Cloud CISO Perspectives post delivered twice a month to your inbox, <a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/resources/google-cloud-ciso-newsletter-signup\" track-name=\"sign up for our newsletter\" track-type=\"inline link\" track-metadata-eventdetail=\"cloud.google.com/resources/google-cloud-ciso-newsletter-signup\">sign up for our newsletter</a>. We’ll be back in a few weeks with more security-related updates from Google Cloud.</p>\n   </div>\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文回顾了 2025 年主要的云安全和人工智能进展与挑战，强调了谷歌云在保护云基础设施、构建安全人工智能、赋能人工智能驱动防御等方面的努力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文回顾了 2025 年主要的云安全和人工智能进展与挑战，强调了谷歌云在保护云基础设施、构建安全人工智能、赋能人工智能驱动防御等方面的努力。",
  "summary": "本文摘自谷歌云的“ 云 CISO 视角 ”，回顾了 2025 年的云安全以及人工智能不断演进的角色。文章强调，人工智能已开始赋予防御者优势，尽管威胁行为者也在采用人工智能。谷歌云致力于通过人工智能简化运营并增强安全性，既包括保护人工智能系统本身，也包括利用人工智能提升防御能力。本次回顾围绕五个关键领域展开：保护云、保护人工智能、人工智能赋能防御、威胁情报和构建可信云。每个部分都提供了简要概述，并指出了相关文章和资源。文章最后展望了 2026 年，强调了威胁行为者的持续创新以及主动防御的必要性。",
